# Football Match Prediction: Techniques, Data, and Research Gaps

**A comprehensive literature review exploring machine learning techniques used to predict soccer match outcomes.**

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-gold.svg?style=for-the-badge)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
